<refsection>
	<title>Description</title>
	<para>
		<command>fbcat</command> takes a screenshot using the framebuffer device. The produced image is in PPM format.
		Note that redirection of standard output to a file or another process is needed since fbcat will refuse to write
		it's output directly to the terminal.
	</para>
</refsection>

